<view class="page-shell">
  <view class="hero-card">
    <view class="hero-eyebrow">Weekly Work</view>
    <view class="hero-title">把周报这件事，压缩成手机上能快速完成的动作。</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">首版先保留本人周报查看、保存草稿和提交审核，先把提交流程跑通。</view>
    <view class="meta-row">
      <view class="meta-pill">建议周次 {{currentWeekNo}}</view>
      <view class="meta-pill">记录 {{list.length}} 条</view>
    </view>
    <view class="button-row" style="margin-top: 24rpx;">
      <button class="primary-button" bindtap="handleCreate">新建本周周报</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="panel-card">
    <view class="section-title">我的周报</view>
    <view class="section-note">如果后端按权限返回更多记录，这里仍以移动端本人使用为主。</view>
    <view wx:if="{{loading}}" class="empty-state">周报列表加载中...</view>
    <view wx:elif="{{!list.length}}" class="empty-state">还没有周报记录，可以先新建本周草稿。</view>
    <block wx:else>
      <view
        wx:for="{{list}}"
        wx:key="id"
        class="list-card"
      >
        <view class="card-title-row">
          <view class="card-title">{{item.weekNo}}</view>
          <view class="status-pill">{{item.statusText}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="card-meta">工作计划：{{item.workPlanPreview || '未填写'}}</view>
        <view class="card-meta">工作内容：{{item.workContentPreview || '未填写'}}</view>
        <view class="card-meta">提交时间：{{item.submitTimeText}}</view>
        <view class="card-meta">创建时间：{{item.createTimeText}}</view>
        <view class="button-row" style="margin-top: 18rpx;">
          <button class="ghost-button" data-id="{{item.id}}" bindtap="handleOpen">查看并编辑</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>
</view>
